{"readme":"<h1 class=\"title\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://github.com/thibauts/remove-orphan-vertices\">remove-orphan-vertices</a><div class=\"contrib\"></div></h1>\n<h3 id=\"removes-orphan-vertices-in-a-simplicial-complex\">Removes orphan vertices in a simplicial complex</h3>\n<p>Completely reindexes positions and removes ununsed vertices along the way.</p>\n<h2 id=\"install\">Install</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"lang-bash\"><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source shell\"><span>$&#xA0;npm&#xA0;install&#xA0;remove-orphan-vertices</span></span></div>\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"usage\">Usage</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"lang-javascript\"><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>var&#xA0;removeOrphanVertices&#xA0;=&#xA0;require(&apos;remove-orphan-vertices&apos;);</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>var&#xA0;mesh&#xA0;=&#xA0;{&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;cells:&#xA0;[</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;[0,&#xA0;2,&#xA0;3]</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;],</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;positions:&#xA0;[&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;[0,&#xA0;0,&#xA0;0],</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;[1,&#xA0;0,&#xA0;0],&#xA0;//&#xA0;&lt;-&#xA0;unused</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;[1,&#xA0;0,&#xA0;0],</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;[0,&#xA0;1,&#xA0;0],</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;[0,&#xA0;0,&#xA0;0]&#xA0;&#xA0;//&#xA0;&lt;-&#xA0;unused</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;]&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>}</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>mesh&#xA0;=&#xA0;removeOrphanVertices(mesh.cells,&#xA0;mesh.positions);</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>console.log(mesh);</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>/*</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>{&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;cells:&#xA0;[</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;[0,&#xA0;1,&#xA0;2]</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;],</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;positions:&#xA0;[</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;[0,&#xA0;0,&#xA0;0],</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;[1,&#xA0;0,&#xA0;0],</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;[0,&#xA0;1,&#xA0;0]</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;]&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>}</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>*/</span></span></div>\n</code></pre>\n"}